@{bg fill}@{fg filltext} Edit palette of ''                  | ]@{fg text}@{bg background}
  __________________________________
 [__________________________________]
               Palette               
 +----------------------------------+
 |                 @{bg shadow}                 @{bg background}|
 |@{bg shine}                 @{bg background}@{bg fill}                 @{bg background}|
 +----------------------------------+
 [   Copy   ][   Swap   ][  Spread  ]
